OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with bright or sunny
OL,6,Fspells and only the odd shower during
OL,7,Fthe morning. Cloud will increase
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain following, some heavy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe night will continue
OL,12,Fcloudy with outbreaks of locally heavy
OL,13,Frain. The rain will begin to ease
OL,14,Ftowards the morning.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FCloudy with rain at first,
OL,17,Fthis soon clearing east then becoming
OL,18,Fmostly dry with bright spells and the
OL,19,Fodd afternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
